## ANOVA arranjo fatorial

### pacote usados

::: {.cell hash='ANOVAFATORIAL_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-1_1c6424c287191fea9af7a044db2279c5'}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(gsheet)
library(tidyverse)
library(DHARMa)
library(emmeans)
library(multcompView)
library(multcomp)
```
:::


### Importar dados


::: {.cell hash='ANOVAFATORIAL_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-2_995587513f8d82d1c3c59437dd3734ba'}

```{.r .cell-code}
li <- gsheet2tbl("https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1bq2N19DcZdtax2fQW9OHSGMR0X2__Z9T/edit#gid=2023059672")
```
:::


### visualizar


::: {.cell hash='ANOVAFATORIAL_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-3_7edfa2d14ae9701d2f0931796dea7980'}

```{.r .cell-code}
li |> 
  ggplot(aes(factor(dose), severity, color = factor(dose)))+
  geom_jitter(width = 0.1)+
  facet_wrap(~ treat)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](ANOVAFATORIAL_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-3-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::


### modelo anova fatorial


::: {.cell hash='ANOVAFATORIAL_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-4_3b9859c9e850f08818dbd489f365c795'}

```{.r .cell-code}
m1 <- lm(severity ~ treat*factor(dose),
         data = li)
summary(m1)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```

Call:
lm(formula = severity ~ treat * factor(dose), data = li)

Residuals:
      Min        1Q    Median        3Q       Max

(Intercept)                      0.29210    0.02731  10.695 1.07e-08 ***

factor(dose)2                   -0.24201    0.03863  -6.265 1.13e-05 ***

Multiple R-squared:  0.8131,	Adjusted R-squared:  0.7781

```
:::
:::


### Checar as premissas


::: {.cell hash='ANOVAFATORIAL_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-5_d0ba9055b7160df0e5cf5d5b7ebf40fd'}

```{.r .cell-code}
plot(simulateResiduals(m1))
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](ANOVAFATORIAL_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-5-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::


### Estimando a m√©dia dos tratamentos
para comparar as colunas (fungicida)

::: {.cell hash='ANOVAFATORIAL_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-6_ccee005401dd7caa6fc16672113a52b3'}

```{.r .cell-code}
means_m1 <- emmeans(m1, ~ treat | dose)
means_m1
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
dose = 0.5:
 treat        emmean     SE df lower.CL upper.CL
 Ionic liquid 0.2921 0.0273 16  0.23420   0.3500
 Tebuconazole 0.0210 0.0273 16 -0.03690   0.0789

dose = 2.0:
 treat        emmean     SE df lower.CL upper.CL
 Ionic liquid 0.0501 0.0273 16 -0.00781   0.1080
 Tebuconazole 0.0202 0.0273 16 -0.03768   0.0781

Confidence level used: 0.95 
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
cld(means_m1)
```

